{"tid":1647468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自殺個案數據分析","createTime":"2019-10-11T18:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T03:42:42.000Z","uid":141060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7301701362f714b84edbec83d3c5f577c09c1151","tid":1647468,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"最近大家都十分關心近四個月以來的不明死亡，我永遠認為數字是不會說謊的。為了了解數據，我翻查了民間就今年以來對自殺數據的統計，以及死因裁判處年報的數據。<br />\n<br />\n其中之一，我本人以至大家，肯定對浮屍發現十分在意，我特意比對了一下數字，發現由6月至今的淹溺死亡個案比往年多，當中女性浮屍更異常地多過過去三年每年總和。<br />\n<br />\n另外，年輕自殺死亡的數字亦異常地多，今年6月至今，已經有100名10-19歲青少年自殺死亡，30-59歲有171人，比較過去三年數據，可以發現四月內已接近全年數字。<br />\n<br />\n還有一樣令我相當好奇，今年9月，10-19歲自殺個案竟然有12宗(圖表沒有顯示)，翻查其他月份，每個月亦只有1至4宗，9月卻突然增至12宗，其中之一是油塘發現的15歲少女。<br />\n<br />\n數字永遠不會說謊，我不會去猜測背後原因，只將數字呈現在大家眼前，但數據反應了事情的不尋常。當然，要深入分析這些數據是需要很長時間，但數據告訴我們，已經響起警號，數字的增加，代表很可能有不尋常的事情發生了，令到數據出現波動。<br />\n<br />\n至於大家如何看這些數字，留待大家自行判斷。<br />\n<br />\n*2019年6月至今數據來自民間根據警方及新聞公布統計<br />\n*2016-2018年數據來自死因裁判處年報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQwkNT5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQwkNT5.jpg&h=49386d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#數據不會說謊<br />\n#電腦無PHOTOSHOP之類所以DEISIGN係差啲<br />\n#警暴<br />\n#自殺個案<br />\n#年輕人自殺愈來愈多<br />\n#浮屍<br />\n#死因<br />\n#刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nby 非凡人物  Facebook"},{"pid":"cedab390375123a50dbb9f5856c7634a3b134ab2","tid":1647468,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:58:34.000Z","msg":"係咪應該搵埋2014同2019的精神健康統計數據<br />\n睇下兩次運動的精神健康水平同自殺數字係咪合符比例"},{"pid":"0acf072d5f5c3d63033dfa9b4857b2439782e687","tid":1647468,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c4eebd51683913d7191ae92194f65fb620175328","tid":1647468,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:00:36.000Z","msg":"巴打好感激你<br />\n<br />\n呢個係重炮"},{"pid":"c98c8c7e915b0ac0730d19ae2b21a14310835b93","tid":1647468,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28381c4787ce2fd5b2e18d96f756bd95f86f4ab7","tid":1647468,"uid":319421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:03:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"39f04012c921dcff24761617d179b356de624483","tid":1647468,"uid":183405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:06:19.000Z","msg":"巴打做實事 支持"},{"pid":"e79b961e01555e182474f6975b992717ce6fcf66","tid":1647468,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:55:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1vHuRRgKjPs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1vHuRRgKjPs&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uE5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=d091e731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1vHuRRgKjPs</a>"},{"pid":"da13649d8e3e2f17c09bd5ad846b997a134660fd","tid":1647468,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:02:41.000Z","msg":"謝謝"},{"pid":"68e7eebf99668ea7baa942f7829be400465755e0","tid":1647468,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:42:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Vicariousshame/status/1183433040715845632?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVicariousshame%2Fstatus%2F1183433040715845632%3Fs%3D20&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uE5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=4b9b5106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVicariousshame%2Fstatus%2F1183433040715845632%3Fs%3D20&h=4ad1d2aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Vicariousshame/status/1183433040715845632?s=20</a>"}]}